## 2. Phase Plan — 6 Phases

### Cấu trúc mới

```
Nguồn Gốc → Thử Lửa → Trỗi Dậy → Đỉnh Cao → Suy Tàn → Kết Thúc
```

### Phase "Kết Thúc" — Nội dung gì?

Phân tích từ 3 script mẫu:

**Genghis Khan Lv13 (death chapter):**
```
- Death event: horse accident → fever → dies at 65
- Legacy scorecard: "a fifth of the earth's land mass, from Pacific to Europe"
- Burial detail: no grave marker, ordered himself, horses driven over site
- Circular callback: "You came from nothing. You returned to nothing."
- Final line: "And now you are history."
```

**Baldwin IV (last chapters):**
```
- Death event: dies at 24, leprosy consumed everything
- Aftermath: "2 years after your death, the French knight will lose Jerusalem"
- Legacy: the kingdom he held together falls apart
- Callback: back to the numb arm from Level 1
```

**Caesar Lv12 (conclusion):**
```
- NO new death event (assassination was Lv11 = Suy Tàn)
- Legacy reflection: "dismantled the old Republic"
- Aftermath: "destroyed by the very men he had empowered"
- Callback: "from an observant boy in the slums to the architect of a new world"
```

### Phase "Kết Thúc" — Quy tắc

| Nội dung | main_key_data? | Ví dụ |
|---|---|---|
| **Death scene** (nếu chưa cover ở Suy Tàn) | ✅ main | Genghis: horse accident → fever → dies |
| **Burial/funeral details** | sub (texture) | No grave, horses over site, soldiers killed |
| **Legacy scorecard** | sub (texture) | "A fifth of earth's land mass" |
| **Aftermath** — world AFTER them | sub (texture) | "2 years later, Jerusalem falls" |
| **Circular callback** | sub (texture) | "You came from nothing" |

**2 trường hợp:**

**Trường hợp A:** Death chưa cover ở Suy Tàn → Kết Thúc CÓ main_key_data
```json
{
  "phase": "Kết Thúc",
  "main_key_data": ["Dies at 65 after horse accident and fever in Gansu mountains"],
  "sub_key_data": ["No grave marker", "Horses driven over burial site", 
                    "Legacy: a fifth of earth's land mass", "From nothing to nothing"]
}
```

**Trường hợp B:** Death đã cover ở Suy Tàn (Caesar: assassination = Lv11) → Kết Thúc main_key_data = []
```json
{
  "phase": "Kết Thúc",
  "main_key_data": [],
  "sub_key_data": ["Legacy: dismantled the Republic", "Destroyed by men he empowered",
                    "From observant boy to architect of world order"]
}
```

### Mapping 3 nhân vật vào 6 phases

**Genghis Khan (13 chapters):**
| Phase | Chapters | Events |
|---|---|---|
| Nguồn Gốc | Lv1-2 | Birth, father poisoned/orphaned |
| Thử Lửa | Lv3-4 | First kill, captured/escape |
| Trỗi Dậy | Lv5-7 | Alliance, betrayal, proclaimed Khan |
| Đỉnh Cao | Lv8-11 | Great law, Jin Dynasty, reckoning, Khwarezm erased |
| Suy Tàn | Lv12 | Last campaign, body failing |
| Kết Thúc | Lv13 | Death at 65, no grave, legacy scorecard |

**Baldwin IV (11 chapters):**
| Phase | Chapters | Events |
|---|---|---|
| Nguồn Gốc | Lv1-2 | Numb arm, leprosy diagnosis |
| Thử Lửa | Lv3 | Boy king at 13, court vultures |
| Trỗi Dậy/Đỉnh Cao | Lv4 | Montgisard miracle — 375 vs 26,000 |
| Suy Tàn | Lv5-9 | Rotting throne, iron will, court factions, blind king |
| Kết Thúc | Lv10-11 | Death at 24, Jerusalem falls 2 years later |

**Caesar (12 chapters):**
| Phase | Chapters | Events |
|---|---|---|
| Nguồn Gốc | Lv1 | Golden cage, Subura slums |
| Thử Lửa | Lv2-3 | Sulla's purge, pirate capture |
| Trỗi Dậy | Lv4-6 | Weeping at Alexander, debt engine, triumvirate |
| Đỉnh Cao | Lv7-9 | Gaul conquest, Rubicon, civil war/Cleopatra |
| Suy Tàn | Lv10-11 | Dictator arrogance, assassination |
| Kết Thúc | Lv12 | Legacy reflection (main_key_data = []) |

> [!NOTE]
> Baldwin IV có Suy Tàn rất dài (5 chapters) vì bệnh leprosy = slow decline. Genghis có Đỉnh Cao dài (4 chapters) vì nhiều conquests. Caesar có Trỗi Dậy dài (3 chapters) vì political rise phức tạp. → Phase plan linh hoạt theo nhân vật.

